# Remap Exclusion List for Win32MetadataScraper
#
# Tags/types listed here will never be auto-remapped, even if the AST discovers
# a typedef-tag relationship. These fall into categories:
#
# 1. Semantic overrides: auto-discovery picks the wrong name because the manual
#    remap uses a C# primitive or different public name.
# 2. Ambiguous targets: the tag has multiple typedef names and auto-discovery
#    picks one that is not the intended public API name.
# 3. Fundamental types: COM/WinRT interface types that should never be renamed.
#
# Format: one tag name per line. Lines starting with # are comments.

# ── Primitive/semantic mappings (manual remap maps to C# primitives) ──────────
# These tags are mapped to C# primitive types like IntPtr, long, etc.
# Auto-discovery would map them to their C typedef name instead.
_LARGE_INTEGER
_ULARGE_INTEGER
_OLD_LARGE_INTEGER
OLD_LARGE_INTEGER
INT_PTR
UINT_PTR
LONG_PTR
ULONG_PTR
DWORD_PTR
SIZE_T
SSIZE_T
LPARAM
WPARAM
LRESULT
SHANDLE_PTR
__int3264
DBLENGTH
DBROWOFFSET
DBROWCOUNT
DBCOUNTITEM
DBORDINAL
DB_LORDINAL
DBBKMARK
DBBYTEOFFSET
DB_UPARAMS
DB_LPARAMS
DBHASHVALUE
DB_DWRESERVE
DB_LRESERVE
DB_URESERVE
TAPIHWND
NDR_CCONTEXT
RO_REGISTRATION_COOKIE

# ── Pointer remaps (manual maps to different pointer types) ───────────────────
# These don't follow the simple typedef-tag pattern
PBOOL
LPBOOL
PBOOLEAN
LPBOOLEAN
PUINT_PTR
PULONG_PTR
PSLIST_ENTRY
PBSTR
LPBSTR
LPLDT_ENTRY
PLSA_HANDLE
PDEVPROPTYPE
PVDS_ADVANCEDDISK_PROP
PREGHANDLE
PRTM_ENTITY_EXPORT_METHOD

# ── GUID/built-in type remaps ────────────────────────────────────────────────
_GUID
DEVPROPGUID

# ── Opaque handle/pointer remaps (mapped to IntPtr) ──────────────────────────
_ACTIVATION_CONTEXT
_HIDP_PREPARSED_DATA
_PROC_THREAD_ATTRIBUTE_LIST
_PSP
_TP_CLEANUP_GROUP

# ── MIDL union struct remaps (nested type renames) ───────────────────────────
# These use :: qualified names that auto-discovery doesn't handle correctly
D3D11_AUTHENTICATED_PROTECTION_FLAGS
_GDI_NONREMOTE
_GDI_OBJECT
_RemotableHandle
_userCLIPFORMAT
_userHBITMAP
_userHENHMETAFILE
_userHGLOBAL
_userHMETAFILE
_userHMETAFILEPICT
_userHPALETTE
_userSTGMEDIUM
_wireSAFEARRAY_UNION

# ── COM interface names that must never be remapped ──────────────────────────
IUnknown
IDispatch
IClassFactory
IMarshal
IMoniker
IStream
IStorage
IEnumUnknown
IEnumString
IEnumMoniker
ISequentialStream
IPersist
IPersistStream
IAdviseSink

# ── Known conflict targets (auto picks wrong typedef) ────────────────────────
# These are documented in auto-type-remappings-plan.md
_RTL_CRITICAL_SECTION
_RTL_SRWLOCK
_RTL_CONDITION_VARIABLE
_RTL_BARRIER
tagSTGMEDIUM
_IMAGE_RUNTIME_FUNCTION_ENTRY
_STRING
